    "Prompt design.",
    "To ensure that the next token is obvious (criterion 1), we design three text completion tasks where the next token x n+1 can be easily inferred from the prompt x 1.",
    "In describing the tasks, we use Chinese as an example language.",
    "Translation task.",
    "Here the task is to translate the preceding non-English (e.g., French) word to Chinese."
  ]
